    Example react-querybuilder output:
    ```json
    {
        "combinator": "and",
        "rules": [
            {"field": "age", "operator": ">", "value": 30},
            {"field": "status", "operator": "=", "value": "active"},
            {
                "combinator": "or",
                "rules": [
